      "variant": "main",
      "html": "<h4>Activity</h4>\n<p>A person took some medicine but does not remember how much. Concerned that she took too much, she has a blood test every hour for several hours.</p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n  <colgroup>\n    <col width=\"127\">\n    <col width=\"140\">\n  </colgroup>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <p><strong>\\(t\\),</strong>&nbsp;<strong>time (hours)</strong></p>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p><strong>\\(m\\),</strong>&nbsp;<strong>medicine (mg)</strong></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <p>&ndash;3</p>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p><br></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <p>&ndash;1</p>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <p>0</p>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>100</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <p>1</p>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>50</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <p>2</p>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <p>25</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"51df55c0-6fe8-49af-be14-93d69eae2652\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\">\n      <li>Answer the following questions.<br><br>\n        a. Time \\(t\\)&nbsp;is measured in hours since the blood test, and amount of medicine in her body, \\(m\\), is measured in milligrams. What is the decay factor? That is, what is \\(b\\)&nbsp;in an equation of the form \\(m=a\\cdot b^t\\)? What is \\(a\\)?</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p> \\(b=\\frac12\\), \\(a=100\\)</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"2647ff5a-cf0f-41c0-bb43-79f5b08dde16\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\">\n      <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"2\" type=\"a\">\n        <li>Find the amounts of medicine in the patient&rsquo;s body when \\(t\\)&nbsp;is &ndash;1 and &ndash;3.</li>\n      </ol>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p>When \\(t\\)&nbsp;is &ndash;1, \\(m\\)&nbsp;is 200.<br>\n      When \\(t\\)&nbsp;is &ndash;3, \\(m\\)&nbsp;is 800.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"9c22f250-2405-4385-9f77-9b2642d252f6\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"2\">\n      <li>What do \\(t=0\\) and \\(t=-3\\) mean in this context?</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p> \\(t=0\\) means the time the doctor did the first blood test. \\(t=-3\\) means 3 hours before the doctor did the first test.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"cb82b480-623e-4b79-9a5d-7648a93df089\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"3\">\n      <li>The medicine was taken when \\(t\\)&nbsp;is &ndash;5. Assuming the person did not have any of the medication in her body beforehand, how much medicine did the patient take?</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p>3,200 mg. Each hour, this is cut in half. After being halved 5 times, it leaves 100 mg, the amount of medicine in the person&rsquo;s body when \\(t=0\\).</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-fire-event=\"Reveal1\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"4\">\n      <li>Plot the points whose coordinates are shown in the table. Make sure to draw and label tick marks on the axes.</li>\n    </ol>\n    <p><img height=\"296\" src=\"https://k12.openstax.org/contents/raise/resources/bd9e16f57c87cb863d69fea1d8f03d9f67d48df6\" width=\"300\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-prompt\">\n    <p>Write down your answer, then select the <strong>Solution</strong> button to compare your work.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-content\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"Reveal1\">\n  <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n  <p><img alt class=\"img-fluid atto_image_button_text-bottom\" height=\"220\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://k12.openstax.org/contents/raise/resources/87c0825791421cf128a96a1b9eabd7e5cd7ccd97\" width=\"300\"></p>\n</div>\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"5a89aa91-ac46-43e1-aee6-c7000b31c629\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"5\">\n      <li>Based on your graph, when do you think the patient will have:\n        <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" type=\"a\">\n          <li> 500 mg of medicine remaining in her body</li>\n        </ol>\n      </li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p>For example: Between 2 and 3 hours before the patient first had her blood tested</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<!--Text Entry Interaction Start -->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"521b36a3-ce92-4c88-a86f-aad8418328ec\" data-fire-event=\"eventShow\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\">\n      <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"2\" type=\"a\">\n        <li>No medicine remaining in her body</li>\n      </ol>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <p>Compare your answer:\n    </p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Sometime after 10 hours. The amount of medicine falls below 0.1 mg after about 10 hours and might be too small to be detectable after that point.</li>\n      <li> Eventually, all of the medicine will be out of the patient&rsquo;s body (but the mathematical model for the amount of medicine does not reach 0).</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Interaction End -->\n<br>\n<h4>Extending Your Thinking</h4>\n<br>\n<!-- \"Start \"Are you Ready for More? click to reveal.  If you have more than one on a page, you will need to change the Data-fire/data-wait-for-events for each set.-->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta\" data-button-text=\"Are you ready for more?\" data-fire-event=\"RFM1\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-content\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-cta-prompt\">\n    <!-- INSERT ANY VALID HTML HERE -->\n  </div>\n</div>\n<!--Start interaction.  If multiple interactions appear under \"are you ready for more?, they should all have matching \"data-wait-for-event\", which should also match the \"data-fire-event\" for the button. Note in this sample, they are all RFM1-->\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"efa47442-a864-46c7-a7d3-9c7d50cbd664\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"RFM1\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <p>Without evaluating them, describe each of the following quantities as close to 0, close to 1, or much larger than 1.</p>\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\">\n      <li>\\(\\frac1{1-2^{-10}}\\)<br>\n      </li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>close to 1</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"d085a6f8-ffda-4797-86f2-2e9b78f1ea97\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"RFM1\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <p><br></p>\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"2\">\n      <li>\\(\\frac{2^{10}}{2^{10}+1}\\)<br>\n      </li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>close to 1</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"775abf5f-520a-4448-8801-31c9c1587da4\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"RFM1\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <p><br>\n    </p>\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"3\">\n      <li>\\(\\frac{2^{-10}}{2^{10}+1}\\)<br>\n      </li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>close to 0</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"cf19e324-fd08-44f8-ba82-e1d5c46d25c9\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"RFM1\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <p><br></p>\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"4\">\n      <li>\\(\\frac{1-2^{-10}}{2^{10}}\\)</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li> close to 0</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"os-raise-ib-input\" data-button-text=\"Solution\" data-content-id=\"08832851-d46d-4df1-b5c1-fbf9aa9e30ea\" data-schema-version=\"1.0\" data-wait-for-event=\"RFM1\">\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-content\">\n    <p><br></p>\n    <ol class=\"os-raise-noindent\" start=\"5\">\n      <li>\\(\\frac{1+2^{10}}{2^{-10}}\\)</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-prompt\">\n    <p>Enter your answer here:</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"os-raise-ib-input-ack\">\n    <p>Compare your answer:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li> much larger than 1</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<br>\n<!--End interaction-->"
    }
  ]
}